            <title>[HBASE-2818] Cannot force a region to close when it has no RS entry in META</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2818</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have a region that&apos;s open on a server, but META thinks it&apos;s not deployed anywhere. I get the following when trying to close it:&lt;/p&gt;

